OL,3,CThousands of bar staff to be trained
OL,4,Cto deal with spiking incidents
OL,6,FWorkers in the night-time economy will
OL,7,Fbe instructed on how to prevent cases,
OL,8,Fsupport victims and help "collect
OL,9,Fevidence" by spring next year, Number
OL,10,F10 said.
OL,12,FIt comes as the Sir Keir Starmer
OL,13,Fsummons chief constables, transport
OL,14,Fbosses and industry executives to
OL,15,FDowning Street on Monday to urge a co-
OL,16,Fordinated response to "this cowardly
OL,17,Fact".
