OL,3,CThousands of bar staff to be trained
OL,4,Cto deal with spiking incidents
OL,6,FLabour pledged in its manifesto to
OL,7,Fintroduce a new offence for spiking,
OL,8,Fbut there was no detail in the King's
OL,9,FSpeech this year about a specific
OL,10,Fcrime, though it promised to ensure an
OL,11,Fimproved police response to cases.
OL,13,FHowever, Sir Keir will reaffirm his
OL,14,Fcommitment to creating a new offence
OL,15,Fon Monday, which the government says
OL,16,Fis part of its promise to halve
OL,17,Fviolence against women and girls in
OL,18,Fthe next decade.
