OL,3,CThousands of bar staff to be trained
OL,4,Cto deal with spiking incidents
OL,6,FIt is unclear when the legislation
OL,7,Fwill be introduced, but ministers and
OL,8,Fofficials are understood to be working
OL,9,Fto bring it forward as soon as
OL,10,Fpossible.
OL,12,FOn Monday, the government will
OL,13,Fannounce 10,000 workers in the
OL,14,Fhospitality industry will be trained
OL,15,Fto deal with incidents by next spring
OL,16,Fas part of an expansion of a scheme
OL,17,Fpiloted from December.
