OL,6,FMeanwhile, Sir Keir will hear from
OL,7,Fpolice and industry leaders at a
OL,8,Fmeeting in Downing Street about
OL,9,Ftactics already being used.
OL,11,FPlain clothes officers are being
OL,12,Fdeployed in areas around bars and
OL,13,Fclubs to spot predatory behaviour,
OL,14,Fwith Chief Constable Jason Hogg of
OL,15,FThames Valley Police due to set out
OL,16,Fhow his force is implementing such
OL,17,Fmeasures.
