OL,3,CThousands of bar staff to be trained
OL,4,Cto deal with spiking incidents
OL,6,FSir Keir said: "My government was
OL,7,Felected on a pledge to take back our
OL,8,Fstreets, and we will never achieve
OL,9,Fthis if women and girls do not feel
OL,10,Fsafe at night.
OL,12,F"Today, I will bring together police
OL,13,Fchiefs, heads of industry and
OL,14,Ftransport bosses to demand coordinated
OL,15,Faction to stop women being targeted,
OL,16,Fwhether they are out with friends or
OL,17,Fsimply travelling home.
OL,19,F"Cracking down on spiking is central
OL,20,Fto that mission.
