OL,3,CThousands of bar staff to be trained
OL,4,Cto deal with spiking incidents
OL,6,F"We know it can be incredibly
OL,7,Fdifficult for victims to come forward
OL,8,Fto report this awful crime, and these
OL,9,Fcases can be very hard to prosecute.
OL,10,FWe must do more to bring the vile
OL,11,Fperpetrators who carry out this
OL,12,Fcowardly act, usually against young
OL,13,Fwomen and often to commit a sexual
OL,14,Foffence, to justice."
OL,16,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said:
OL,17,F"Spiking is a disturbing and serious
OL,18,Fcrime which can have a damaging and
OL,19,Flong-lasting impact on victims.
